    "The significance derives from the fact that aggressive driving on the road leads to traffic accidents.",
    "'Emotion identification' can be done utilizing facial expressions, voice, and text, as well as biosignals such as the electroencephalograph (EEG), blood volume pulse (BVP), electrocardiogram (ECG), electromyogram (EMG), galvanic skin response (GSR), respiration (RSP), and combination of more than one signal.",
